Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:04.95,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1550.134,355.101)}我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:05.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把從各個村子收集到的泥土暫時存放在舊城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:08.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在各村莊祇要做到抽出這一步就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但馬匹只有這些 小麥也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要做這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:16.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了 處男
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我的確是處男
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}大事不好了 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但別說我處男啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有輛奇怪的馬車在接近我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的馬車？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:33.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是聖日爾曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:35.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是奧爾特的大貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精靈族的男人快點藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,女精靈不藏起來也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:50.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,來者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:58.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個壓抑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:00.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地方還真是壓抑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和想像中不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:06.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想像中的是有更多閃亮閃亮 閃亮閃亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:10.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在清淨的森林裡 和煦的陽光下 人跡罕至的神聖泉水邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全裸的精靈少年們和精靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:15.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,搞來搞去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:16.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聖日爾曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:23.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會親自來這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:26.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼 漂流者麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:31.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是舊精靈居留地的稅務計算官 米爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:34.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在被精靈們抓到…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一股處男的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了和漂流者見面而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:41.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:43.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出來吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:45.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊對啊 出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 男精靈也太少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:51.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,藏起來了吧 出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個 他們現在並不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不在是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們去哪裡了 你快給我一五一十地說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就吃了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:07.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們去解放矮人 然後把男精靈都帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:08.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:11.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去製造槍啊 機關鎗什麼的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:11.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,槍…槍…槍…槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然拿去讓矮人族製造
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火…火…火…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火藥呢 火藥那方面怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火藥已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經在拚命地製造了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:27.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 奧爾特完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:30.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是叫來了何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬍子已經夠麻煩的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這下可變得更加麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,紫 在搞毛啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:41.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得亂七八糟了啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:45.05,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,公主大人 怎麼了公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:46.43,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,紫…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.19,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,這是我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.72,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,別管我了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.19,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,總之在他們回來之前我就在這等著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.68,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,快款待我們 盛大地款待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:09.30,difters-op,,0,0,0,,發動引擎 給我動力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:13.77,difters-op,,0,0,0,,踩下油門 奏響福音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.52,difters-op,,0,0,0,,歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:14.52,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}sing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:28.24,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾馳 在這蜿蜒曲折中突進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:31.16,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:34.66,difters-op,,0,0,0,,這是颶風般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.83,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.21,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.67,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:48.51,difters-op,,0,0,0,,即使已超速 也無法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:53.30,difters-op,,0,0,0,,引擎全開 全身繃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.06,difters-op,,0,0,0,,和我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.06,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:07.53,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾馳 在這蜿蜒曲折中突進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.95,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:14.37,difters-op,,0,0,0,,這是颶風般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.25,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.79,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.17,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是黑王及其臣下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:38.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說出 要滅亡人類 這種事情 口氣還真不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然飼養 馴服隸屬於我們的飛龍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:45.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作為自己的家犬來使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:48.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是在小看我們麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是黑王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,排到隊列中便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:01.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,面對作為青銅龍的我 竟然敢出言不遜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙算老幾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:08.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 你是誰都沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:12.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼樣子或是什麼種族也都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是飢餓的小哥布林還是你 都一律平等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:21.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,給我面向這邊 身披破布的白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要我把你蹂躪成破布麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:40.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:49.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我們一同前進麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還是與他們一起邁向黃泉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有旁觀這個選項 青銅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:58.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,給我回答 青銅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:02.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:07.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:12.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,軍團…軍團算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎你的加入 青銅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:21.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你的姿態比起令人畏懼更多的是受人輕蔑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:24.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有加入我們軍團的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:31.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,向來話少的你居然開口了啊 土方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:36.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們黑王的力量是生命的增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:39.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,治癒的能力也祇是從中衍生出來的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:45.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 無限制的增殖會生出腫瘤 直至死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不用每次都向我下跪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要使用力量了 你們往對面去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,祇要是活物便能無盡地使其增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:22.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,細胞也好 糧食也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對於與黑王為敵的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,若以黑王作為軍團指揮官來考慮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:31.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的力量應該是噩夢般的東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,傷患能立即痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.38,0:07:37.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就連那些本來無法行動和瀕死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也能夠立馬返回隊伍作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:44.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,糧食和柴火都可以無限制地增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,後勤這一概念將不復存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼要讓他們來耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,食物的話 自己做出來不就好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:08:00.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為 我並非永恆的神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯普京 事情辦好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:10.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這本來就是我專業領域內的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這不過是非常單純的體系而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再單純一點對他們來說也比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:19.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,象徵是眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原型是拜火教和古老的瓦爾納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.67,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}註：拜火教，基督教誕生之前中東最有影響的宗教。瓦爾納，即印度的種姓制度。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,埃及 以及凱爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:26.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,混合了其中的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 還有這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以羅馬字的基礎或者說是完整照搬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:35.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要讓它們理解 還是需要時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:38.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你問我到底想讓它們做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是多個種族的共同體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,狗頭人 哥布林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,今後肯定會有各種各樣其他的種族加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:48.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要施行一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,創造出共通的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,創立統一宗教並進行教化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:57.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原始農業 共通文字 統一宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:08:59.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一直嘲笑為怪物的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,將把人類代替掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,從而在地面上誕生出文明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:09.74,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你可算是醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:20.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,北壁 是龍騎兵把你救回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾德萊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,化成了鹽塊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那些傢伙給燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:33.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去把他們殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:37.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你太小看他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要對漂流者掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我就會殺掉他們的 順順利利地把他們殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去幫吉爾德萊報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等待時機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:55.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,最後肯定會讓你如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:04.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個武士 要把他殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,傾盡我全力地把他燒死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把他燒得連炭都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,她如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說頭蓋骨差點被掀開 但是很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王大人替她治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:24.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在被帶到這裡之前死掉也毫不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個名為豐久的漂流者頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:32.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似並不會因為對手是女人就手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:41.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那也是按照自己的標準行事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:45.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,之後被手下留情的對象會變得怎樣和他毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:49.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他的存在本身 就是自我滿足的集合體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:52.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是被稱為武士的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.53,0:10:54.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是如此 才無法讓人小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:57.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自那群傢伙出現以來的800年間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:01.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們就是在那狹小的島國裡不分晝夜地互相廝殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外就無事可做的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:08.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,面對其末裔 我們俄羅斯不還是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為貞德被欺負所以生氣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,皇女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:20.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:28.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！快住手！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:35.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王 停下來 快讓他們停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！讓他們停下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不願和我們一夥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就祇是塊肉罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:50.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,給我閉上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…哪邊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:10.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個公務員一樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個管理戶口的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:16.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能贏得了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:25.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？火槍？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.06,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火槍是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃麼那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:30.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火槍啊 火槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:33.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們這不是一直都在吃麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫我們也想戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再拿多點酒和飯菜過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:42.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了東西就太過精神了吧 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？要幹架麼 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊？有意見麼 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個工廠理應還有大量糧食的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:54.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米小姐 有追加的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一百人份量的湯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直接拿水給他們喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:04.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們越吃越壯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 矮人果然很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:17.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏拉 你為什麼笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人回歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,睡前故事裡面的矮人回歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:28.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噗哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噗哈你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:33.75,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,那湯裡不是有牛馬的肉嗎 這也吃得下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:37.17,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,在薩州 祇要是肉都吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:42.56,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,打仗時上頓不接下頓 餓起來連野狗也得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:44.52,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\an8}夠了 你別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:54.34,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:56.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫義經的人真的是好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:59.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在聽麼 老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我在聽 我在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:08.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本來 突然之間居然叫我射扇子什麼的很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能中才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:14.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還叫我去射水手 是不是有病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:18.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是讓人幹不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,酒品還是差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,會讓人誤會的 快把衣服穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:24.85,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,在薩州我也是這樣喝的x
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.49,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.67,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,老爺子 在吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.58,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,蟲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.42,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也給我們弄點酒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:40.58,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,前略 織田家的各位身體還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.30,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,我是前右府
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.75,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,現在想起來 各位還真是聽我的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:47.95,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,你們真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.50,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,但是光秀 你給我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:54.29,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:57.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡 把那個所謂的火槍給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:08.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 是鐵筒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:11.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是把鐵捲起來製造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:14.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個扳機的機關和弩有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:20.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這根鐵棒會彈入這個圓盤中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:24.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是射擊用的裝置麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把手只是單純的木頭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這個到底是要怎麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:35.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那個叫做火槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:38.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓火藥在筒中炸裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以讓鉛彈射出的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:43.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是武器麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,射出鉛彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:49.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道那個火藥是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:53.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要特意做些這麼麻煩的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弓和弩不是很好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這個不行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這點我也是不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:06.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用弓的話既能無聲無息地進攻又不用這樣大費工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要執著於火槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 聲音和硝煙也是必要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說才會好懂一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:17.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,槍火是火槍開槍時候的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:20.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是你被瞄準了的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:22.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且火槍的訓練時間很短
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:26.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天還是農民的人 第二天甚至能打倒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:31.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 這傢伙並非笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是個專攻戰鬥的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:37.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,遠射程外加威力大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:40.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是槍真正的優勢並不全是這兩點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:44.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,槍可以使殺人 殺意以及罪惡感簡便化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:48.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟祇要輕輕扣動扳機 誰都能簡單地成為士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:53.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是全民皆兵的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:57.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這可說不得 說不得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:07.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的這個鐵管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:11.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫火槍什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們國家的冶煉技術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:16.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強還是能說得上厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是比不上我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去 第一根
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…喂 昨天才開始做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已經能做出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有圖紙的話還不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過實物都擺在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:34.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們肯定能做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:35.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:38.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過應該沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:43.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個工房都市全力運轉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西能做出多少根來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:50.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這個工房都市可是負責生產奧爾特一半以上的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這還是我們挨餓偷懶的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:56.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們動真格的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:18:01.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 這跟劍和鎧甲有很大區別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然做熟手起來要花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是七八根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後會增加到十根左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:12.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才這麼點啊！虧你這麼有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:16.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還不夠嗎？每天撐死十根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別強人所難了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:19.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這矮人族真的假的 真心厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺擺出了一副陰險的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他偶爾會這樣 別管他就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:34.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久那邊怎樣了 還在吃他的飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:36.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:39.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男的說要運動一下促進消化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:42.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著我們的年輕人去了什麼地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:47.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話沒法區分你們的年輕人和老傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來全部都像大叔一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為什麼詛咒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:51.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也能戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族的戰鬥是一擊必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:04.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是把一切都賭在這斧頭上的一擊的戰法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:06.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮的破甲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:07.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像示現一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,示現…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:15.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,示現流啊 禦本家的年輕二子興起的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我祇專注於體捨流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:20.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼閒工夫去學什麼示現流就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使位於遙遠的世界也有同樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:30.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算身形外貌有區別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:33.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵可是在什麼地方都會產生的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:34.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:36.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:37.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不！你們是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:44.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,繼精靈族之後連矮人族也拉攏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者們下手真是快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:51.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有想過這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:55.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能讓他們做出槍來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼令人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 泥巴拍不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聖日耳曼的馬車在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:12.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人妖大領主伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:12.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:17.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂歐派米 這傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是藝人嗎 倒不如說是人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是聖日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:24.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,支配著奧爾特三分之一土地的大貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:29.98,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,明明本大人特地大駕光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:34.20,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,結果你們從那廢城出來之後遲遲不見回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:37.11,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,等來等去也沒有要回來的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:40.68,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,所以我才親自跑到這髒亂差的地方來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.88,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,快感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:43.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聖日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你有漂流者或者廢棄物的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:50.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉 說得人家像罪犯一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼懷疑不懷疑 我就是漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有我這樣的廢棄物啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:01.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明胸部很大 腦子卻很輕呢你個笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:05.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼要和那個國父成立什麼奧爾特帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真失禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾特可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別說得跟廢棄物所作所為一樣 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:14.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那位國父 阿道夫·希特勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也是貨真價實的漂流者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:20.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,國父創建了高效的官僚主義帝國
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:24.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把世襲的惡習連根拔起 分配了財富
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後又故意製造出「一定數量的差別階級」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:31.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以此來管理民眾 完成中央集權
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:35.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除了獎賞我的土地以外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:37.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的工作可是十分出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:42.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然如何能跟周圍的種族打五十年仗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:46.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前見過和你有同樣眼神的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:50.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既不知道他是誰 也聽不懂他在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙最後被茶壺裡裝滿的火藥給炸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一種怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,松永彈正？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.65,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}\N松永彈正：松永久秀，彈正為官位名。戰\N國時期的武將，日本第一位自爆死的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:03.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 拿我和那種人比？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:07.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙知道我們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:10.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙 不能放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這位聖日耳曼伯爵到此有何貴幹？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:18.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是否有資格和我聯手 我來確認這一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:25.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是頭目 島津豐久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:29.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這傢伙搞不懂到底是男是女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什麼傢伙 奧爾特的手下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:37.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 奧爾特的手下 就是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:38.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還算
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.61,0:22:41.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:45.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,劍很銳利 殺氣卻很鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:46.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有何企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:51.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜 再過個30年就是我喜歡類型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:55.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒辦法了 殺掉你的話就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:22:58.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是身經百戰的銀髮長者還糟糕點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:01.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就怨恨自己的年輕去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:14.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 老頭子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.43,0:23:16.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 阿雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:19.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不行了 站不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:21.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把阿雷斯塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:23.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們什麼都沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:28.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你和那老頭都在我的射程外所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:32.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 我可不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:35.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不出來個遮住半邊臉的單馬尾少年！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:38.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,豐久殿下 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:45.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我手下的高手正在測試你們的頭目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:47.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 會變得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:52.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人… 救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:55.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:57.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊豐久 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:23:59.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:01.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就把他們揍了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:05.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這兒也有個不知是男是女的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:07.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,來者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.65,0:24:09.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,賣國賊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:11.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,賣國賊？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:15.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 我是到這來把奧爾特賣給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.08,0:24:18.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可是跳樓大甩賣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:19.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把國家…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:21.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,賣出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.21,0:24:23.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 要賣掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:25.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在還有點商品價值
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:29.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要亡國 也有亡國的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:33.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是被諸國軍隊包圍 在城下俯首稱臣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.80,0:24:38.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,國土四分五裂讓人怎麼受得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:41.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要讓我們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,趁奧爾特還存有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.19,0:24:49.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必須趁現在給奧爾特致命一擊讓其高效地崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:52.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:25:03.30,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your away 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:25:03.30,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}開拓你的道路 向著拂曉之空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.59,0:25:07.55,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodythirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.59,0:25:07.55,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:12.52,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:12.52,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼熱翻騰的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:19.65,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:19.65,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高舉心無旁騖的大義之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.73,0:25:31.12,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.73,0:25:31.12,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}熱浪就如晃蕩的交響樂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.33,0:25:41.13,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声は響く三日月を
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.33,0:25:41.13,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌聲 在新月之夜下蕩漾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.34,0:25:44.46,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}この身　焚べた炎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.34,0:25:44.46,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.63,0:25:46.93,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.63,0:25:46.93,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破曉的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.13,0:25:50.97,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.13,0:25:50.97,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的衝動 閃耀著
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:56.14,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your away 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.05,0:25:56.14,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}開拓你的道路 向著拂曉之空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.27,0:26:00.44,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodythirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.27,0:26:00.44,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.52,0:26:05.19,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滲む痛み引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.52,0:26:05.19,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}與被染紅的痛楚一同
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.28,0:26:12.28,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果てない今日を踏んだ大地へ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.28,0:26:12.28,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}衝破無盡的今日 邁向新大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.41,0:26:19.50,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}栄光を歌う peace at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.41,0:26:19.50,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歌頌榮光 終歸和平
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.67,0:26:23.63,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更なる大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.67,0:26:23.63,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高舉更為雄壯的大義之旗
